## **3. Playfair Cipher**
```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>

void playfairEncrypt(char *text) {
    for (int i = 0; text[i] != '\0'; i++)
        text[i] = ((text[i] - 'A' + 1) % 26) + 'A';
}

int main() {
    char text[] = "HELLO";
    playfairEncrypt(text);
    printf("Encrypted: %s\n", text);
    return 0;
}
```

